{"title":"Python 学习笔记","uid":"42081f6a72dae0aca4242b63068167ff","slug":"python-notes","date":"2021-06-04T20:12:30.616Z","updated":"2021-06-09T14:31:20.889Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/python-notes.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<p>如果出现多个 <code>return</code>, 以第一个出现的 <code>return</code> 为准!</p>\n<p><code>float(&#39;inf&#39;)</code> 代表无穷大, 可以认为是 infinity.</p>\n<p><code>range()</code> 的 ‘step’ 不能是 -1.</p>\n<p>In Python, slices are handled safely with respect to indices that are out of bounds. 但是单个 <code>[k]</code> 这样的就不行!</p>\n<h3 id=\"Logical-Operators\"><a href=\"#Logical-Operators\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Logical Operators\"></a>Logical Operators</h3><p>To evaluate the expression <code>&lt;left&gt; </code> and <code>&lt;right&gt;</code>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Evaluate the subexpression <code>&lt;left&gt;</code>.</li>\n<li>If the result is a false value v, then the expression evaluates to v.</li>\n<li>Otherwise, the expression evaluates to the value of the subexpression <code>&lt;right&gt;</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>To evaluate the expression <code>&lt;left&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;right&gt;</code>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Evaluate the subexpression <code>&lt;left&gt;</code>.</li>\n<li>If the result is a true value v, then the expression evaluates to v.</li>\n<li>Otherwise, the expression evaluates to the value of the subexpression <code>&lt;right&gt;</code>.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"BitwiseOperators\"><a href=\"#BitwiseOperators\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"BitwiseOperators\"></a>BitwiseOperators</h3><ul>\n<li><p><code>x &lt;&lt; y</code> Returns <code>x</code> with the bits shifted to the left by <code>y</code> places (and new bits on the right-hand-side are zeros). This is the same as multiplying <code>x</code> by <code>2**y</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>x &gt;&gt; y</code> Returns <code>x</code> with the bits shifted to the right by <code>y</code> places. This is the same as //‘ing <code>x</code> by <code>2**y</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>x &amp; y</code> Does a “bitwise and”. Each bit of the output is 1 if the corresponding bit of <code>x</code> AND of <code>y</code> is 1, otherwise it’s 0.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>x | y</code> Does a “bitwise or”. Each bit of the output is 0 if the corresponding bit of <code>x</code> AND of <code>y</code> is 0, otherwise it’s 1.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>~ x</code> Returns the complement of <code>x</code> - the number you get by switching each 1 for a 0 and each 0 for a 1. This is the same as <code>-x - 1</code>.</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>x ^ y</code> Does a “bitwise exclusive or”. Each bit of the output is the same as the corresponding bit in <code>x</code> if that bit in <code>y</code> is 0, and it’s the complement of the bit in x if that bit in y is 1.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"zip-function\"><a href=\"#zip-function\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"zip( ) function\"></a>zip( ) function</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> a <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> b <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">7</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> zipped <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>b<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>     <span class=\"token comment\"># 打包为元组的列表</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>c<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>              <span class=\"token comment\"># 元素个数与最短的列表一致</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token builtin\">zip</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>zipped<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>          <span class=\"token comment\"># 与 zip 相反，*zipped 可理解为解压，返回二维矩阵式</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">6</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>","text":"如果出现多个 return, 以第一个出现的 return 为准! float(&#39;inf&#39;) 代表无穷大, 可以认为是 infinity. range() 的 ‘step’ 不能是 -1. In Python, slices are handled safely ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.9k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":12,"path":"api/categories/Python.json"},{"name":"Note","slug":"Python/Note","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Python/Note.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Logical-Operators\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Logical Operators</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#BitwiseOperators\"><span class=\"toc-text\">BitwiseOperators</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#zip-function\"><span class=\"toc-text\">zip( ) function</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"ClanLU","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"Leetcode 刷题资源","uid":"d833f85b7b257d1481c14b935cb505a4","slug":"leetcode-resources","date":"2021-06-05T19:57:25.618Z","updated":"2021-06-11T18:17:08.682Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/leetcode-resources.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"Data Structure Introduction to Data Structure by Leetcode 部分刷题顺序中文 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":68,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Leetcode","slug":"Leetcode","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Leetcode.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Resources","slug":"Resources","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Resources.json"}],"author":{"name":"ClanLU","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210313122054101.png","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}}},"next_post":{}}